dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning for Vilas County, Wisconsin in 2019. The following features are included: 'Vilas_Zoning_2019' and 'Vilas_Shoreland_2019'. For General: [The zoning classification defined at the parcel level, but typically managed in larger units.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://data-vilas.opendata.arcgis.com/]
